These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, subway, bus, jet-ski
1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person eating mango is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Transport   | subway  | scooter     | bus   | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, prince, siglo, old-henry
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the prince-smoker##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Cigar   | siglo    | prince      | swisher | old-henry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, montecristo, oliveros, siglo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | siglo | oliveros   | montecristo |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

