.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, entrepreneur, electrician, coach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the coach##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the entrepreneur is on the left of the social-worker##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the right of the coach##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | coach | entrepreneur | social-worker  | electrician      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

