.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea, bellflower, tulip
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Flower   | tulip | bellflower | azalea | amaryllis |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

