.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, april, february
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Birthday   | november  | april | february           | october   |

