.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, september, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking sprite is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice  | coffee | water   |
| Birthday        | september | june | february    | april |

