.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-14::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, onion, peach, watermelon
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, polish, german, egyptian
1. the person eating blueberry is the polish##1
2. the thai is on the right of the polish##1
3. the person eating onion is the german##1
4. the person eating peach is on the left of the german##1
5. the german is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry | peach  | onion  | watermelon |
| Nationality   | polish   | thai | german | egyptian   |

