2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the malaysian##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian     | argentine | egyptian |
| Hobby         | reading | skydiving | traveling   | chess   |

