.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, software-developer, doctor, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the freelancer is on the left of the doctor##1
4. the mechanic is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | freelancer | doctor | software-developer | mechanic   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 